cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on 3D shape reconstruction and completion using learned implicit functions, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also introduces a new approach using deep features, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the reconstruction of articulated humans, which could potentially fall under neural networks (cs.NE).
